text: “OH GUYS? WHO FEELS LIKE GETTING UP TO SOME MISCHIEF?”
“MAYBE A LITTLE MONKEYING AROUND?”
“I DO, I DO,
“AW I LOVE MONKEYS!”
FIVE LITTLE MONKEYS JUMPING ON THE BED
ONE FELL DOWN AND BUMPED HIS HEAD
MAMA CALLED THE DOCTOR AND THE DOCTOR SAID
NO MORE MONKEYS JUMPING ON THE BED! HAHAHA.
“OH BOY, THIS IS FUN.”
“HEY, I LOVE JUMPING ON MY BED! HAHAHA”
FOUR LITTLE MONKEYS HANGING FROM A TREE
ONE FELL DOWN AND HURT HER KNEE
DADDY SAW WHAT HAPPENED AND HE SAID TO ME
NO MORE MONKEYS CLIMBING UP THE TREE! HAHAHA!
“WELL, I GUESS DADDY KNOWS BEST!”
“MONKEYS DO LOVE TO HANG FROM TREES HAHAHA!”
THREE LITTLE MONKEYS RUNNING ON THE FARM
ONE FELL DOWN AND HURT HIS ARM
FARMER SHOUTED AT THEM LIKE A LOUD ALARM
NO MORE MONKEYS RUNNING ON MY FARM! HAHAHA
THAT FARMER SURE WAS MAD!”

“I GUESS MONKEYS BELONG IN THE ZOO,
NOT ON THE FARM!”
TWO LITTLE MONKEYS FIGHTING IN THE SNOW
ONE FELL DOWN AND HURT HER TOE
TEACHER CAME OUTSIDE AND SHE SAID ‘UH OH’
NO MORE MONKEYS FIGHTING IN THE SNOW! HAHAHA
“WOW, BEING A MONKEY SURE IS FUN.
THAT SNOW IS TOO COLD FOR A MONKEY, THAT’S WHY THEY LIVE IN THE JUNGLE”
ONE LITTLE MONKEY CLIMBING VERY HIGH
HE FELL DOWN AND HURT HIS EYE
MAMA CAME TO HELP HIM WHEN SHE HEARD HIM CRY
NO MORE MONKEYS CLIMBING VERY HIGH!! HEHE.
“OH BOY, I GOTTA BE MORE CAREFUL FROM NOW ON!!”
YOU NAUGHTY LITTLE MONKEYS! HAHAHA. THAT WAS FUN!”
